{%- comment -%} 
  To add a new personal page for a person:
    – add a new person record in people.yaml, give it a unique ID and a name for corresponding html page
    – duplicate _template.html in this folder, change filename to the same that you specified earlier in people.yaml
    – change person_id value marked as 'CHANGE_THIS' inside the to match the ID or a newly added person
{%- endcomment -%}